contactmgmt

Interface Contact

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContactImpl

    public interface Contact
    A contact is a person we are making business with or may do in the future. Contacts have an ID (unique), a name (probably unique, but maybe not), and notes that the user may want to save about them.
